11:59.052 --> 12:00.929
Hold on.
Now, did you call her?

12:00.929 --> 12:02.639
I did not.

12:02.639 --> 12:05.808
But when you said it was Joel,
I remembered that his mother

12:05.808 --> 12:09.062
