to get her nails done

12:09.062 --> 12:10.897
just like I do.
[ Bell jingles ]

12:10.897 --> 12:13.608
Hey, Mrs. Howard.
Barbara: Hello, Amber.

12:18.738 --> 12:20.782
Aren't you
my son's teacher?

12:20.782 --> 12:22.283
