or ship it?

12:33.878 --> 12:36.339
This is just like
the one in my apartment.
This is gonna be easy.

12:36.339 --> 12:38.883
Me and Tariq have to go in that
thing like three times a month.

12:38.883 --> 12:40.510
Maybe you should move.

12:40.510 --> 12:42.011
[ Grunting ] Yeah.

12:42.011 --> 12:44.889
Tariq says he is "practicing"
his credit score.

12:44.889 --> 12:47.934
[ Chuckles ]
Apparently, 380 isn't a good ‐‐

12:47.934 --> 12:50.144
Unh.
[ Whistles ]

12:50.144 --> 12:54.232
Oh, no. "Don't touch.
