12:54.232 --> 12:56.859
Uh, okay.
What's that say?

12:56.859 --> 13:00.697
"End of the Road"?
"It's So Hard to Say Goodbye"?

13:00.697 --> 13:02.699
What? "Motownphi‐‐"

