13:15.336 --> 13:17.130
Aah! Ohh.
Aah! Ooh.

13:17.130 --> 13:19.924
We're going to ‐‐
[ Click ]

13:19.924 --> 13:21.509
N‐o‐o‐o‐o!

13:21.509 --> 13:23.594
[ Indistinct conversations ]

13:29.892 --> 13:31.769
Can you give me
something bold?

13:31.769 --> 13:35.857
Something that...
