13:55.668 --> 13:57.879
School starts at 8:00.

13:57.879 --> 14:00.048
Is there a reason
for this?

14:00.048 --> 14:04.427
Well, nosy, I start
my shift at my job at 9:30,

14:04.427 --> 14:07.388
