to drop him off before that

14:07.388 --> 14:10.349
and go straight to work instead
of going home or whatever.

14:10.349 --> 14:12.143
Right, right.

14:15.063 --> 14:17.815
Can I get some rhinestones
that say,

14:17.815 --> 14:20.568
"I'm not afraid of
awkward interactions"?

14:20.568 --> 14:22.612
Literally or
metaphorically?

14:22.612 --> 14:25.615
'Cause I can do that design.
It'll just be $50 extra.

14:25.615 --> 14:27.116
Fifty ‐‐

14:27.116 --> 14:28.951
Well, I hear what
you're saying, um, Amber.

14:28.951 --> 14:32.246
Y‐Your son needs to be
at school at 8:00.

14:32.246 --> 14:34.207
He's missing a lot
of vital learning.

14:34.207 --> 14:37.585
Word? I thought y'all just be
playing with blocks and stuff.

14:37.585 --> 14:40.379
No. This isn't daycare.
By the time he comes in,

14:40.379 --> 14:43.299
we're already working on
primary reading and math.

14:43.299 --> 14:45.259
He's always struggling
to keep up.

14:45.259 --> 14:47.637
Oh.

14:47.637 --> 14:49.222
I didn't know that.

14:49.222 --> 14:50.890
Yeah, I would hate for him

14:50.890 --> 14:53.142
to fall behind and
have to retake the grade.

14:53.142 --> 14:56.104
I don't want that, but
that's as much up to you

14:56.104 --> 14:57.605
as it is up to me.

14:57.605 --> 14:59.482
I get you.

14:59.482 --> 15:02.068
I don't want him
to fall behind.

15:02.068 --> 15:03.653
He's a smart kid.

15:03.653 --> 15:05.071
Very.

15:05.071 --> 15:06.614
Okay.

15:06.614 --> 15:08.491
I'll bring him at 8:00
from now on.

15:11.202 --> 15:12.870
Barbara:
[ Clears throat ]

15:12.870 --> 15:14.789
It's kinda nice.

15:16.958 --> 15:18.251
Word.

15:18.251 --> 15:19.877
‐Ooh.
‐What in the ‐‐ What's going on?

15:19.877 --> 15:23.256
‐What in the world?
‐It's so hot! I'm gonna frizz!

15:23.256 --> 15:26.259
‐[ Gasps ]
‐Janine, what did you do?!

15:26.259 --> 15:28.219
Lookin' like
who shot John.

15:28.219 --> 15:31.264
Barbara, look, I know you told
me to let it go, but I couldn't.

15:31.264 --> 15:32.974
Jacob helped me
open the breaker.

15:32.974 --> 15:35.518
It was a chance to support
a strong Black woman.

15:35.518 --> 15:37.895
The breaker?! Janine!
You can't do this stuff!

15:37.895 --> 15:40.022
What had you come to work today
