15:40.022 --> 15:42.483
Look, I ‐‐
I just have ‐‐

15:42.483 --> 15:44.402
‐Oh. Ooh. Okay.
‐I feel lightheaded.

15:44.402 --> 15:45.987
‐Are you okay?
‐Did you eat today?

15:45.987 --> 15:47.822
Because I know
you didn't have lunch.

15:47.822 --> 15:50.074
Jacob: And you didn't have
any breakfast.

15:50.074 --> 15:52.702
Okay. We're losing her. Do
I have your consent to slap you?

15:52.702 --> 15:54.662
‐Oh!
‐There she goes. She's out.

15:54.662 --> 15:56.205
‐Um...
‐Y'all feel this heat?

15:56.205 --> 15:57.915
Oh, my God!
She pale like a zombie!

15:57.915 --> 15:59.959
You know, they eat
the hottest people first.

15:59.959 --> 16:01.335
Let me back my tasty ass up.

16:01.335 --> 16:03.212
Okay, I'm gonna get some
water out of the fridge.

16:03.212 --> 16:04.463
Uh, hopefully
it's still cold!

16:04.463 --> 16:06.090
Oh, my God! My branzino!
Barb, excuse me!

16:06.090 --> 16:07.758
I'll be back!
She'll be okay!

16:10.344 --> 16:12.680
[ Children shouting playfully
in distance ]

16:14.849 --> 16:16.726
[ Exhales sharply ]

16:16.726 --> 16:19.145
Where's my class?
Is ‐‐ Is everyone okay?

16:19.145 --> 16:21.772
Obviously,
everyone's not okay.

16:21.772 --> 16:23.858
You're in
the nurse's office.

16:23.858 --> 16:26.068
But everybody else
is fine.

16:26.068 --> 16:28.738
[ Children squealing
and laughing ]

16:34.619 --> 16:36.746
[ Squealing and laughter
continue ]

16:36.746 --> 16:40.082
Melissa: He used him as
a shield. Did you see that?

16:40.082 --> 16:42.668
They are so happy.

16:42.668 --> 16:44.879
He's climbing again.

16:44.879 --> 16:48.382
Oh, look who's back
in the land of the living.

16:48.382 --> 16:50.426
Who opened
the fire hydrant?

16:50.426 --> 16:53.554
Well, as Melissa would say,
snitches get stitches.

16:53.554 --> 16:55.890
That is correct,
but I am not talking to you

16:55.890 --> 16:58.226
on account of you
killing my branzino.

16:59.560 --> 17:01.479
[ Clears throat ]

17:03.940 --> 17:07.318
Barbara: Ooh.
What's going on here?

17:08.611 --> 17:12.573
So that's it, huh?
I, uh, gave it my all,

17:12.573 --> 17:14.450
passed out,
and ruined the school day?

17:14.450 --> 17:17.161
Oh, you tanked.
You tanked, Janine.

17:17.161 --> 17:19.956
You took the whole school down
with you. It was impressive.

17:19.956 --> 17:21.832
Look. I know.
I should've stopped.

17:21.832 --> 17:23.918
I'm sorry.
I just felt so bad

17:23.918 --> 17:26.254
