17:40.893 --> 17:43.271
Because
it's the opposite.

17:43.271 --> 17:47.149
We care so much,
we refuse to burn out.

17:47.149 --> 17:49.694
If we burn out,
who's here for these kids?

17:49.694 --> 17:52.863
That's why you gotta
take care of yourself.

17:52.863 --> 17:54.323
What is with you today,
anyway?

17:54.323 --> 17:57.118
You ‐‐ You're normally
bananas, but...

17:57.118 --> 17:59.662
I don't know. Just some stuff
at home, I think.

17:59.662 --> 18:01.330
Oh. Okay.

18:01.330 --> 18:03.291
See, that's the other thing
me and Barbara learned.

18:03.291 --> 18:04.959
All that at‐home stuff ‐‐
you gotta ‐‐

18:04.959 --> 18:06.836
[Clicks tongue] ‐‐
