a whole nother

18:08.421 --> 18:09.964
Panera's box of problems.

18:09.964 --> 18:12.300
I think you mean
Pandora's box.

18:12.300 --> 18:14.635
No, I'm pretty sure
it's Panera's box.

18:14.635 --> 18:16.804
[ Children squealing
and laughing ]

18:19.473 --> 18:22.268
Thank you for your help
earlier, Mrs. Howard.

18:22.268 --> 18:23.644
I feel like
a better communicator.

18:23.644 --> 18:25.146
Mm.

18:25.146 --> 18:27.690
Well, if you're gonna
keep doing this job,

18:27.690 --> 18:29.859
awkward interactions
come with it,

18:29.859 --> 18:32.069
so you've got to learn
how to say what you need

18:32.069 --> 18:33.904
to get what you want.

18:33.904 --> 18:36.032
Mm‐hmm.

18:46.417 --> 18:47.793
Hey, Jaden,
don't drink that.

18:47.793 --> 18:50.004
Mnh‐mnh.
Don't drink that. No.

18:50.004 --> 18:52.798
Tariq:
Hey, I'm not here right now.
Leave a message after the beat.

18:52.798 --> 18:55.551
[ Beatboxing ]
♪ This Tariq ♪

18:55.551 --> 18:59.055
[ Beep ]
Hey, Tariq. Um, listen.

18:59.055 --> 19:02.224
You need to look
at the budget tonight.

19:02.224 --> 19:05.645
No more waiting.
No more practicing.

19:05.645 --> 19:07.229
Tonight.

19:10.608 --> 19:12.026
[ Knock on door ]

19:12.026 --> 19:13.569
Hey.
Hey.

19:13.569 --> 19:15.279
Hey.
Have you eaten?

19:15.279 --> 19:18.366
Oh. No. The, um, lunch lady
gave me that can of peaches,

19:18.366 --> 19:21.077
