19:43.891 --> 19:47.186
Like...4:00.

19:47.186 --> 19:49.438
Yeah. All true.

19:49.438 --> 19:51.774
So let's go eat.

19:51.774 --> 19:54.402
Let's. Okay.
[ Chuckles ]

