21:02.470 --> 21:04.346
[ Chuckles ]

21:05.973 --> 21:08.642
Mm! You sure
follow orders.

21:10.853 --> 21:12.688
Just doing my job.

21:12.688 --> 21:15.357
[Mocking Amber]
"Well, you doing it well."

